OL,3,CMeningitis: What can people do to
OL,4,Cprotect themselves?
OL,6,FWords by Lois Smith
OL,8,FTwo students from Kent have died,
OL,9,Fwhile several more are in hospital,
OL,10,Fafter an outbreak of meningitis in the
OL,11,FCanterbury area.
OL,13,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,14,Fhas said the outbreak is likely to be
OL,15,Fmeningococcal, caused by the bacterium
OL,16,FNeisseria meningitidis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773748973
OL,3,CMeningitis: What can people do to
OL,4,Cprotect themselves?
OL,6,FSome students at the University of
OL,7,FKent have been given antibiotics while
OL,8,Fothers are in hospital. The specific
OL,9,Fstrain of meningitis has not yet been
OL,10,Fidentified.
OL,12,FMeningococcal disease is serious and
OL,13,Fcan progress rapidly, but it is still
OL,14,Frare, and outbreaks have become much
OL,15,Frarer with improved vaccination
OL,16,Fprogrammes and public awareness.
OL,18,FWhat you need to know about meningitis
OL,19,F` including symptoms, risks and how to
OL,20,Fprotect yourself.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
